==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Formica
<hw>For*mi"ca</hw> <pr>(f⟦ocir⟧r*m⟦imac⟧"k⟦adot⟧)</pr>, <pos>prop.
n.</pos> <ety>[a trademark.]</ety> <def>A thermosetting plastic material
composed of melamine resin, having good heat and chemical resistance,
and commonly used as the surface layer in laminated sheets employed as
coverings for counter tops, walls, or furniture.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Formicaroid</ent>⟦br⟧
